text: I enjoy being physically active or using mechanical tools & machines. I am practical and enjoy being rewarded for the results I get.
I am precise, logical and curious about how things work. I enjoy being able to solve problems and learn new things.
I am original, innovative and creative. I enjoy using my imagination, coming up with new ideas, and expressing myself in words, music, art, or dance.
I am friendly and outgoing. I enjoy helping people by teaching, explaining the things I do, or giving advice.
I am a leader and enjoy being in charge. I am confident and like to take risks and make the decisions.
I am efficient and organized. I enjoy getting into details, working with numbers, and following procedures & standard methods.
I am resourceful and efficient. I enjoy managing my time, others’ time, and the materials needed to get the job done.
I like to learn new things, mostly through study or school. I enjoy writing or talking about the things I know.
I like to think about things that are abstract, theoretical, or conceptual. I enjoy work that challenges my mind.
I am a social person and like to share my ideas. I enjoy working with the public and connecting with people through speaking or writing.
I like to solve problems with logic. I prefer to be systematic and methodical to get to the right answer.
I enjoy fixing things with my hands. I like to know how things work and how to keep them working well.
I like to make decisions based on data. I enjoy calculating and analyzing things to get to an answer.
I enjoy using science, technology, engineering, or math principles to solve problems or create new solutions. I like to apply what I know to practical situations.
